 and markets ngls and transports and stores crude oil and refined products marathon petroleum was founded on june   and is headquartered in findlay oh expand key people marathon petroleum corp board of directors nametitle current board membership gary r heminger  chairman  chief executive officer marathon petroleum corp frank m semple  director marathon petroleum corp j michael stice  independent director marathon petroleum corp abdulaziz fahd alkhayyal  independent director marathon petroleum corp james e rohr  independent director marathon petroleum corp steven a davis  independent director marathon petroleum corp john p surma  independent director marathon petroleum corp donna a james  independent director marathon petroleum corp birch evans bayh  independent director marathon petroleum corp david a daberko  lead independent director marathon petroleum corp charles e bunch  independent director marathon petroleum corp expand all executives gary r heminger chairman  chief executive officer donald c templin president timothy t griffith chief financial officer  senior vice president donald w wehrly chief information officer  vice president rodney p nichols evphuman resources  administrative services brian partee directorbusiness development anthony r kenney presidentspeedway segment raymond l brooks senior vice presidentrefining molly r benson secretary chief compliance officer  vp david l whikehart corporate affairs vpsafety  environment c michael palmer senior vpsupply distribution  planning john s swearingen senior vice presidenttransportation  logistics john j quaid vice president  controller frank m semple director thomas kaczynski treasurer  vice presidentfinance thomas m kelley senior vice presidentmarketing john r haley vice presidenttax chuck rice directormedia relations lisa wilson directorinvestor relations dave sauber vice presidenthuman resources  labor relations suzanne gagle vice president  general counsel j michael stice independent director abdulazi