nts refining  marketing speedway and midstream the refining  marketing segment refines crude oil and other feedstocks at its refineries in the gulf coast and midwest regions of the united states purchases ethanol and refined products for resale and distributes refined products through various means including barges terminals and trucks that the company owns or operates the speedway segment sells transportation fuels and convenience products in the retail market in the midwest primarily through speedway convenience stores the midstream segment gathers processes and transports natural gas gathers transports fractionates stores and markets ngls and transports and stores crude oil and refined products marathon petroleum was founded on june   and is headquartered in findlay ohat a glancemarathon petroleum corp south main streetfindlay ohio united states  industryoil  gas productsservicessectorcompanies on the energy servicefiscal year enddecember revenuebsales growthemployeesall values updated annually at fiscal year endvaluationpe currentpe ratio with extraordinary itemspe ratio without extraordinary itemsprice to sales ratioprice to book ratioprice to cash flow ratioenterprise value to ebitdaenterprise value to salestotal debt to enterprise valueprofitabilitygross marginoperating marginpretax marginnet marginreturn on assetsreturn on equityreturn on total capitalreturn on invested capitalefficiencyrevenueemployeeincome per employeereceivables turnovertotal asset turnovercapitalizationtotal debt to total equitytotal debt to total capitaltotal debt to total assetslongterm debt to equitylongterm debt to total capitalliquiditycurrent ratioquick ratiocash ratioboard of directorsgary r hemingerchairman  chief executive officerfrank m sempledirectorj michael sticeindependent directorabdulaziz fahd alkhayyalindependent directorjames e rohrindependent directorsteven a davisindependent directorjohn p surma jrindependent directordonna a jamesindependent directorbirch evans bayh i